            "title": "美軍武器庫存告急？傳白宮急召軍工企業增產",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美軍武器庫存告急？傳白宮急召軍工企業增產\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"617\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Wz_DWVREX8g5F5fEG3GwLA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/08c804f0-196a-11f1-abdf-cc4c374e99cf\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美軍武器庫存告急？傳白宮急召軍工企業增產</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
